code: @SuppressWarnings("unchecked") @Override public final Request indices(String... indices) {     this.indices = indices.     return (Request) this. }
@SuppressWarnings("unchecked") public final Request indicesOptions(IndicesOptions indicesOptions) {     this.indicesOptions = indicesOptions.     return (Request) this. }
@Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     super.writeTo(out).     out.writeStringArrayNullable(indices).     indicesOptions.writeIndicesOptions(out). }
@Override public void readFrom(StreamInput in) throws IOException {     super.readFrom(in).     indices = in.readStringArray().     indicesOptions = IndicesOptions.readIndicesOptions(in). }
